<p>Sets @font_desc as the font description for a <link xref="Clutter.Text">Clutter.Text</link></p><p>The <link xref="PangoFontDescription">PangoFontDescription</link> is copied by the <link xref="Clutter.Text">Clutter.Text</link> actor
so you can safely call pango_font_description_free() on it after
calling this function.</p>

